<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Seraphis IT and Data Solutions</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-800">
  <header class="bg-blue-900 text-white p-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">Seraphis IT and Data Solutions</h1>
      <nav>
        <ul class="flex space-x-4">
          <li><a href="#services" class="hover:underline">Services</a></li>
          <li><a href="#about" class="hover:underline">About</a></li>
          <li><a href="#contact" class="hover:underline">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="text-center py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-800 to-blue-600 text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Empowering Businesses with Secure Cloud Solutions</h2>
      <p class="text-xl">Web Hosting, Cloud VMs, Compliance, Security & Data Intelligence</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="services" class="py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-10">Our Services</h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
        <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded shadow">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Web Hosting</h4>
          <p>Reliable and secure cloud-based web hosting tailored for scalability and performance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded shadow">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">VMs & Container Deployment</h4>
          <p>Deploy and manage virtual machines or containers securely on the cloud.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded shadow">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Compliance & Regulation</h4>
          <p>Ensure POPIA, GDPR and other regulatory compliance with our expert audits and tools.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded shadow">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Security Solutions</h4>
          <p>Protect your applications and network with advanced security tools and monitoring.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded shadow">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Data Mining & Processing</h4>
          <p>Transform your data into insights using cloud-based mining, storage, and dashboards.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded shadow">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">VM Access for Schools</h4>
          <p>Provide high-performance virtual desktops to schools using legacy computers at low cost.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="about" class="bg-gray-100 py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">About Seraphis</h3>
      <p>We are a mission-driven IT firm helping African businesses and institutions modernize through secure cloud services. We believe in efficiency, affordability, and sustainability in tech.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact" class="py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-2xl">
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-6">Get in Touch</h3>
      <form class="space-y-4">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Name" class="w-full p-3 border border-gray-300 rounded">
        <input type="email" placeholder="Email" class="w-full p-3 border border-gray-300 rounded">
        <textarea placeholder="Your message" class="w-full p-3 border border-gray-300 rounded"></textarea>
        <button type="submit" class="bg-blue-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded hover:bg-blue-800">Send Message</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="bg-blue-900 text-white py-6 text-center">
    <p>&copy; 2025 Seraphis IT and Data Solutions. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
